#. type: Title =
#: guide/transaction-spec/functionality/verification.adoc:2
#, no-wrap
msgid "Invoice verification"
msgstr "請求書の検証"

#. type: Plain text
#: guide/transaction-spec/functionality/verification.adoc:5
msgid ""
"This process forms part of the Buyer’s internal business controls. The "
"invoice shall refer to an authentic commercial transaction. Support for "
"invoice verification is a key function of an invoice. The invoice should "
"provide sufficient information to look up relevant existing documentation, "
"electronic or paper, for example, and as applicable:"
msgstr ""
"このプロセスは、購入者の内部業務管理の一部を形成します。 請求書は、認証済みの"
"商取引に言及するものとします。 請求書検証のサポートは、請求書の重要な機能で"
"す。 請求書には、関連する既存の文書（電子文書や紙など）を検索するのに十分な情"
"報が記載されている必要があります。"

#. type: Plain text
#: guide/transaction-spec/functionality/verification.adoc:7
msgid "the relevant purchase order"
msgstr "関連する注文書"

#. type: Plain text
#: guide/transaction-spec/functionality/verification.adoc:8
msgid "the contract"
msgstr "その契約"

#. type: Plain text
#: guide/transaction-spec/functionality/verification.adoc:9
msgid "the call for tenders, that was the basis for the contract"
msgstr "契約の基礎となった入札の呼びかけ"

#. type: Plain text
#: guide/transaction-spec/functionality/verification.adoc:10
msgid "the Buyer’s reference"
msgstr "購入者の身元保証"

#. type: Plain text
#: guide/transaction-spec/functionality/verification.adoc:11
msgid "the confirmed receipt of the goods or services"
msgstr "商品またはサービスの確認済み受領"

#. type: Plain text
#: guide/transaction-spec/functionality/verification.adoc:12
msgid "delivery information"
msgstr "納品に関する情報"

#. type: Plain text
#: guide/transaction-spec/functionality/verification.adoc:14
msgid ""
"An invoice should also contain sufficient information that allows the "
"received invoice to be transferred to a responsible authority, person or "
"department, for verification and approval."
msgstr ""
"請求書には、確認と承認のために、受け取った請求書を責任のある当局、個人、また"
"は部門に転送できるようにするための十分な情報も含まれている必要があります。"
